<section id="about" class="band band-cream">
  <div class="band-inner about-inner about-inner--reverse">
    <div class="about-image-col">
      <%= image_tag 'yamanashi.jpg', alt: 'Kofu, Yamanashi skyline with Mt. Fuji', class: 'about-photo' %>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text-col">
      <h2 class="band-heading"><span>&#128214;</span> My Story</h2>
      <p>
        Write a short intro that frames who you are and how you got here &mdash; a couple of sentences about your background, what drew you to building software, and what excites you about the work.
      </p>
      <p>
        Use this space to give the reader a sense of your voice and perspective before they dive into the project details below.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="band-inner about-inner">
    <div class="about-text-col">
      <h2 class="band-heading"><span>&#128075;</span> About</h2>
      <p>
        I'm a full-stack developer who enjoys building web applications that solve real problems.
        I work with Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, and modern front-end frameworks.
      </p>
      <p>
        Write another paragraph here &mdash; where you&rsquo;re based, what you&rsquo;re working on,
        what you&rsquo;re passionate about, or a hobby you love.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image-col">
      <%= image_tag 'tokyo.jpg', alt: 'Tokyo skyline at night', class: 'about-photo' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
